{"tid":1933421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"誤認是中国人   猶太人在以色列被暴打","createTime":"2020-03-19T09:25:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T09:34:28.000Z","uid":184679,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e4a59843aaddc402c43abcad7c9fd34aa38c5e30","tid":1933421,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:25:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/4PMwHcp1kV9G3flAPHQydg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04NDguNw--/https://s.yimg.com/uu/api/res/1.2/gFJIBS_RtR3aCkstCDgj1g--~B/aD04MjA7dz0xMjAwO3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-/https://media.zenfs.com/zh-tw/newtalk.tw/6494f98533b6bf9b2af69991001499ad\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F4PMwHcp1kV9G3flAPHQydg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTEyNDI7aD04NDguNw--%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fuu%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FgFJIBS_RtR3aCkstCDgj1g--~B%2FaD04MjA7dz0xMjAwO3NtPTE7YXBwaWQ9eXRhY2h5b24-%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fzh-tw%2Fnewtalk.tw%2F6494f98533b6bf9b2af69991001499ad&h=836d1faf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n據《印度斯坦時報》報導，一名印度猶太人在以色列被誤認成中國人，遭到兩名對中國人有有種族歧視偏見的當地人暴打了一頓。被打的男子叫阿薩勒姆辛森(Am-Shalem Singson)，居住在以色列提比里亞市。<br />\n<br />\n辛森在外出時遇到兩名當地人衝著他大喊：「中國人！武漢肺炎！」接著就衝上前對他拳打腳踢，造成他胸部嚴重受傷。<br />\n<br />\n辛森回憶，他拼命向施暴者解釋，自己不是中國人、也沒有感染新冠病毒，但仍未能阻止對方繼續施暴。由於事發當時沒有目擊者，目前警方仍在設法尋找這兩名施暴的嫌疑人。<br />\n<br />\n辛森3年前和家人前往以色列定居。像他們家這樣的印度猶太人，原本多聚居在印度東北部曼尼普爾邦、米左拉姆邦。20世紀末，有部分猶太學者聲稱：此一族群是猶太人裡的瑪拿西 (Marathi)分支，因此將他們認定為猶太人。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AA%A4%E8%AA%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%8C%B6%E5%A4%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E8%A2%AB%E6%9A%B4%E6%89%93-112620276.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.mobi.yahoo.com%2Fnews%2F%25E8%25AA%25A4%25E8%25AA%258D%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%258D%25B0%25E5%25BA%25A6%25E7%258C%25B6%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%259C%25A8%25E4%25BB%25A5%25E8%2589%25B2%25E5%2588%2597%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%259A%25B4%25E6%2589%2593-112620276.html&d=vBgtTLCpkGvyAljQauEZFcjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=21cfe2a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.mobi.yahoo.com/news/%E8%AA%A4%E8%AA%8D%E6%98%AF%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E5%8D%B0%E5%BA%A6%E7%8C%B6%E5%A4%AA%E4%BA%BA%E5%9C%A8%E4%BB%A5%E8%89%B2%E5%88%97%E8%A2%AB%E6%9A%B4%E6%89%93-112620276.html</a>"},{"pid":"06022ffbebacfd4c51d5bcb9839d7d6d406874d3","tid":1933421,"uid":297230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:29:01.000Z","msg":"黑狗偷食，白狗當災<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fb2178314c65c8ba93b2e5f5f1202dd4ebc822a","tid":1933421,"uid":258192,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:29:48.000Z","msg":"辛森在外出時遇到兩名當地人衝著他大喊：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">「中國人！武漢肺炎！」</span></span>接著就衝上前對他拳打腳踢，造成他胸部嚴重受傷。<br />\n<br />\n好想快d升lvl<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n支那人無一個係蘑菇"},{"pid":"02d69c576dcbff874a861f8e03b33502c45007ac","tid":1933421,"uid":297230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:30:14.000Z","msg":"支那武漢肺炎搞到全球排亞"},{"pid":"56974a22f03230c710b83b245acb17839fbe1c26","tid":1933421,"uid":116560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T09:34:28.000Z","msg":"有d人仲話鬼佬分到香港人同中国人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}